1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:18:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>movenpick 真係好食到仆街  乜味都好撚好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 朱古力味濃到不得了仲要有朱古力片做分層，士多啤梨味酸酸甜甜唔假仲要有果肉，焦糖燉蛋味甜而不膩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咖啡味濃到我用成杯咖啡整嚟做雪糕咁，焦糖拖肥味又有焦糖粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主推既tiramisu味簡直係新世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一打開個膜就佩服真係成個tiramisu咁既樣，啲味仲要好有層次，又有嘢咬下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我愛你啊movenpick<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n如果鍾意朱古力味既話, 瑞士chocolate 係好濃好香滑<br />\n佢同tiramisu 都係movenpick 既皇牌"},{"pid":"28be185a669f47d7d468d9f630854e77c918d670","tid":355412,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/172053_14e6e772c802101e6a6c071564c16448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F172053_14e6e772c802101e6a6c071564c16448.jpg&h=f62b6067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n屌 你半男半女黎架<br />\n一隻腳白滑一隻腳咁多毛</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n左邊大脾內側少毛啫<br />\n我對腳多毛成個創意台都知啦"},{"pid":"ae46ae659bef03d656a76f168c1224fa17e6bf75","tid":355412,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:20:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>公司用呢隻雪糕出餐返工日日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCPCS?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪公開飯堂?non-staff有冇得喫?"},{"pid":"b020cddabc8cb46e0446fa3916765cc8ede9d0b3","tid":355412,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:22:14.000Z","msg":"屌咩，中撚晒伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁撚好食架，10分鐘就清左兜野，真係好tiramisu 呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340ac9a439f4a36649eb1d64a9ce5ae14ee1a375","tid":355412,"uid":13996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:22:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/172053_14e6e772c802101e6a6c071564c16448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F172053_14e6e772c802101e6a6c071564c16448.jpg&h=f62b6067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n屌 你半男半女黎架<br />\n一隻腳白滑一隻腳咁多毛</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n左邊大脾內側少毛啫<br />\n我對腳多毛成個創意台都知啦</blockquote><br />\n唔係兩個人黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為有毛係巴打左腳<br />\n冇毛係第2個人隻右腳"},{"pid":"f51cedfea73e99f12422c8225bf762b1ec116589","tid":355412,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:22:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔明點解啲人鐘意maple walnut多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺, walnut 唔係啲咩矜貴果仁 成盒都甜到溜"},{"pid":"d96f6d411ecfb63f351ac7f23bbec576982fe52b","tid":355412,"uid":46358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:23:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/172053_14e6e772c802101e6a6c071564c16448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F172053_14e6e772c802101e6a6c071564c16448.jpg&h=f62b6067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡直係成舊tiramisu 放咗入去咁<br />\n滑到乜咁<br />\n最緊係上面層咖啡<br />\n一定要慢慢食咗佢先食落底<br />\n入面仲有啲biscuit..<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嗯~</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/CMrrzki.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FCMrrzki.gif&h=a36df928&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係屌打哂所有超市盒裝雪糕<br />\n嗰啲咩士多啤梨味呀..死埋一邊啦<br />\n我都好多年冇再食dreyer's 嗰啲次嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nm&ouml;venpick <br />\n依家惠康做梗$120/2pcs <br />\n我用惠康$100 禮劵加$20 就買到<br />\n真係抵到爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCan't agree more"}]}